chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
hola

vamos a el tigre

¿a dónde sigue?
vamos para el elephamte
ok, estoy viendo al elefante ahora

la sierpeniente
bueno, estoy mirando la serpiente ahora

cocodrillo
lo siento, pero el cocodrilo está en distracción, el camino está bloqueado
¿tomamos otra ruta?
el sapo
¡listo! ahora estoy frente al sapo
¿hacia dónde debo ir desde aquí?
el parajo
vale, estoy viendo al loro en el árbol ahora
¿a dónde vamos desde aquí?
tigre

¿dónde debo ir ahora?
el mapa

elephante
estoy de vuelta en la isla con el elefante, ¿y ahora?
giraffe

serpente

treasure chest

si
cool! we're starting at the top right corner with the white dog
look left, see that wooden bench? begin to walk towards it
picnic
not yet, mate! go left and cross the trail toward that florist stand
but don't actually get to the stand, okay?
flowers
love your enthusiasm but make a u-turn, mate
step back to the trail and head towards our white fluffy friend again
cross log
go for it! cross over that branch and keep heading down the map
there's another white dog by a checkered picnic mat
pic nic
yup, that's it! now walk over the mat and head towards the bowl of berries
any in there for a snack?
walk over branch
yes, good move! cross that branch towards the north this time
cross bridge
wait a sec, don't rush off to the bridge yet! circle that green bush from your right side first
after that, head up to the florist stand
circle green brush
well done! now, turn left (west) and walk below the stand until you reach a big bridge
can you see it?
floral shop
perfect! from there continue on, pass that bridge, and walk until you see two elderly people on a bench
pass bridge
great, now head a few steps south, between the old folks and another wooden branch until you reach a green bush
walk to deer
not yet! first, go east between the branch and the bush
go between branch and bush
exactly, just a few steps east from there! see anything familiar?
deer
yes!! you made it! you found the deer, congrats buddy!
walk over log
great! now go south, keep walking until you spot another white dog
it's sitting next to a checkered picnic mat
white dog
perfect! now go past the dog and keep heading south
you'll need to step on the picnic mat and touch the bowl of berries. keep going west after that
step on picnic and grab berries
nice! now, you'll cross another wooden branch, but go north this time
cross wooden  branch
well done! once you cross, avoid touching the green bush
circle it from the right side, on to the florist stand
white dog
right, now go left, pass below the stand until you reach the big bridge
see those two cyclists?
yes
go past the bridge, on your left you'll see two elderly people on a bench
see 'em?
yes
awesome! now, go few steps south from them, you'll be between the old folks and another wooden branch
ok
good job!  now spot the green bush by the end of the wooden branch
i see it go there
perfect, now go east, keep the branch on your left and the bush on your right
go east
you got it! take a few steps east
see anyone new?
deer
that's it! you've reached the final point
well done!
thanks
you're welcome! you did great! ready for another round?
yes
alright! let's start again then, you're back at the top right corner with our white dog friend
hi there! que comience el juego!!
si
awesome! i see a tent on the north side
which direction should i head, buddy?
west
okay, then
i don't see anything towards the west from the tent. could you guide me again?
walk to dog
oh, i gotcha! heading south towards the dog, right next to the fire
what's next?
go to fire
alright, standing right next to the fire
where to next?
go to mushrooms
aha! moving east to the red mushroom
here i am
go around bush to the car
got it! going south around the bush to the blue car
here i am now. what's next, boss?
go to telescope
so i'm heading south again to the blue telescope
go to cabin
heading west to the house surrounded by rocks
where are u
right at the doorstep of the house! *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes\
alright, first head southwest passing under the first tree and cross the second palm tree
make a sharp left turn before you hit the third tree. keep going south
walk to dog
oh yeah, see the brown puppy? stay to the left of it
turn slightly left, then go right, heading south
go to crab\
before that, you need to go between these two rocks
see one big, one small? go right between them till you reach the water
go between these two rocks
exactly, now you see our buddy the red crab? turn right and follow the big rock westwards in the water
turn right and follow the big rock westwards in the water
you're doing great
after the medium rock, turn sharp right when you see this shark, dude. no worries!
turn sharp right when you see this shark, dude. no worries!
perfect, now head back to the land, passing between the medium rock and an awesome tri-color ball
keep heading north
now head back to the land, passing between the medium rock and an awesome tri-color ball
ease slightly left now, aim for that red tent and large speaker up north-west
aim for that red tent and large speaker up north-west
good job, make a nice arc around the tent, then head south
but not too far into the water, okay?
make a nice arc around the tent, then head south but not too far into the water, okay
exactly, turn right just before the water and walk beneath that cool red kayak, going west
turn right just before the water and walk beneath that cool red kayak, going west
great job, now turn 90 degrees right, heading north alongside the kayak
now turn 90 degrees right, heading north alongside the kayak
perfect, keep going towards the little green bush
you're almost there!
keep going towards the little green bush
and you made it, my friend, awesome work! that's your final stop
see, wasn't too bad, right?
it was good
i knew you'd ace it! let's play again sometime
ok
alright, looking forward to it! until then, take it easy
u too
thanks, buddy! catch ya later!
next game
sure thing! i'll let you know when the next game is ready
till then, stay awesome!
